quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  17,109,"Ni akasagwa niipundi yao achililaga, ni jikwajonjechesyaga (Qur’anijo) kulinandiya."
  17,110,"Jilani (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ): “Mum’bendani Allah kapena mum’bendani Ar-Rahmân, nilina lililyose lyachimum’bendele (yalumope), ligongo Jwalakwe jukwete mena gambonembone.” Soni nkanyanyikaga nnope ni (Qur’an ja pa) swala jenu kapena kutulusya nnope maloŵe, nambo kuyani litala lya chilikati chayalakweyo."
  17,111,"Ni m’becheteje kuti: “Lumbili losope lwene alapikwe Allah jwanganalitendela mwanache, soni nganakola jwagaŵana najo pa Uchimwene (Wakwe), soni nganaŵa jwaulesi kwanti nikola jwakunkamuchisya, soni munkusyani kunkusya kwannope!”"
  18,76,"(Musa) jwatite: “Naga nam’busye yachindu chine panyuma pachalakwechi, basi ngasimungunda soni kulongana namwe, pamasile pampochele usulu wakwanila kuumila kukwangu.”"
  18,77,"Basi ni ŵajendelechele ŵanaŵaŵili (pa ulendo wao), mpaka pandema jaŵaichilile ŵandu ŵa m’musi (wa Antwâkia), ŵaŵendile yakulya achimisyene musio, nambo ŵakanile kwakalibuchisya. Basi ni ŵalisimene mwalakwemo lipupa linankusaka kugwa, basi (Khidr) ni jwalijimiche. (Musa) jwatite: “Nkasache, chisimu chene nkagapochelele malipilo (masengo galakwega nitukaasuumiile yakulya).”"
  18,78,"(Khidr) jwatite: “Aku ni kulekangana kwa chilikati cha une nomwe. Sano chinantagulile ngopolelo sya ichindu yanganinkombola kuipililila ata panandi.”"
  19,37,"Basi ni gaatiindeene makuga (ga Akilisito) chilikati chao (pakwamba ya Isa, ŵane kutiji mwanache jwa Nnungu, ŵane nnungu jwene, ŵane jumpepe mwa milungu jitatu), basi ipotesi tiikaŵe ya aŵala ŵaŵakanile yakuja kuonechela pansongano wa lisiku lyekulungwa."
  19,38,"Kaje kupikanichisya ŵanganyao (achimakafilio) ni kulolechesya lisiku lyatachituichilila! Nambo ŵalupuso lelo (pa duniya pano), ali mu kupotela kwakuonechela."
  19,39,"Soni mwatetelani ŵanganyao ya lisiku lyamadandausi, ndema jachichilamulidwa chilamusi (chakwinjila ku Mbepo ni ku Moto), kutendaga ŵanganyao (pa duniya pano), ali nkulilechelela soni ngakukulupilila."
  20,19,"(Allah) jwatite: “Jiponyani mmwe Musa!”"
  20,20,"Ni ŵajiponyisye; basi ajile sai ŵajiweni jisyuchile lijoka lyakwenda mwaluŵilo."
  20,21,"(Allah) jwatite: “Likamulani, soni nkajogopa. Chituliuchisye mu kaŵe kakwe kandanda (kuŵa simbo).”"